<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>wǒ yī shēng zuì dà de shì 迦南439</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ yī shēng zuì dà de shì shì rèn shì yé hé huá,
 wǒ yī shēng zuì měi de lù, shì zhǔ wèi wǒ xìng qǐ,
 tā jiāng wǒ jí zhòng de zuì tóu zài shēn hǎi lǐ,
 tā de xǐ lè hé píng ān, wú yǐ néng xiāng bǐ,
 ō shā lún de méi guī huā, wǒ jīn rèn shì nǐ,
 ō yuán zhōng de fēng xiān huā, wǒ gèng ài mù nǐ,
 ō gǔ zhōng de bǎi hé huā, wǒ shēn shēn ài zhe nǐ,
 nǐ shì wàn gǔ de pán shí, wǒ yī shēng tóu kào nǐ.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>439</hymn_number>
</song>